{
  "stem": "13833.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was absolutely magnificent because it was lit up, not like in Spain.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And eventually, the curator committed suicide because it was such a terrible place to take care of everything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was just too much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was a young man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then there was-- we went to a-- just in August, '39, we went with four students on a so-called autostop tour.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We started out in Geneva and went all the way in-- down to France.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we stopped in Marseilles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we were in a youth camp there, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And it was absolutely wonderful because there were Arabs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There were Jews.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There were Czechs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "There were every kind of young people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And yet nobody said, you're a Jew, you're an Arab.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There was love between the Arab and Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we learned each other's songs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we danced each others' dancing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I mentioned it that we, the young people, could make peace, because we don't know what it is to hate each other.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then we came back--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and we-- to Geneva.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we found out that there was some kind of a Zionist meeting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I never belonged to any kind-- and neither did my family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we went to the beach.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we saw these people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was first of September.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were all on the beach, when suddenly, the microphone screamed that the Germans just overran Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you could have heard a pin dropping [LAUGHS] in the sand, it was so quiet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And these poor people in their bathing suits were running to the phones.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was absolutely-- just stood there cold, that this can happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
